lyrics.stanza:
Draw me, Lord;
Lest these earthly cares consume
My driven soul.
Move me Lord;
As a coursing river turns
Within Thine hands.

Draw me, Lord;
Ev'ry heartbeat tends to drift
My course from Thee.
Draw me, Lord;
I would gladly let Thee win
And yield my sword.

Draw me, Lord;
Oh, Thy love compels me as
An ocean's tide!
Draw me, Lord;
For Thy drawing maketh hearts
To fast pursue.
